[color=#ffff00][size=3]install[/size][/color]

[size=3]for ece users: just put the files "commonTriRaces.slot" in the CME_save folder
then go to the game, open showracemenu (i recommand this mod ([url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33968/?]lossless race change[/url])
take nord race and choose the appropriate slot
DONE!

for non ece users: when you install enhanced character edit for the first time, you need to run the game at least once!
this create the CME_save folder located in your saves folder then [/size][size=3]put the file "commonTriRaces.slot" in the CME_save folder
then go to the game, open showracemenu (i recommand this mod ([url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33968/?]lossless race change[/url])
[size=3]take nord race[/size] and choose the appropriate slot
DONE!

[size=3]for racemenu users just install with your favorite mods manager[/size], in game choose Nord race (exept eva Mendez that need the redguard race) and activate the preset
[/size][size=3]DONE![/size]

[color=#ff0000][color=#e06666][size=5]remember that this is only a preset so you can edit it at your convenience!![/size][/color]
[color=#cc4125][size=3]I try to do the closest I can do so![/size][/color]
[size=3]If you come here to say " it's ugly, it's bad, it's blabla, plz, don't lose your time[/size][/color][size=5][color=#ff0000]!![/color] [color=#ff0000][size=3](and mine)[/size][/color]
